channel.title: Xclusive - Where exclusive dreams are being share together
channel.description:
[center][size=10pt][u]Introductions[/u][/size][/center] [size=12pt][font=arial]Greeting fellow users my name is John . Xclusive is server I've been working on so far , my goal for this server is an economy and pvp server with a large player base, a great friendly community, and flawless game-play, a place that make players feel happy and joyful playing Xclusive . I am the only developer and wish to have a team to work along with me . Teamwork and learning is the core-value , When I've been playing on the servers before i told myself that this interest me and i wanna learn it so i take my effort and time to learn about creating a server and choosing a base and it was Project insanity i start from a scratch i am not sure of anything but i ask for help and see how people done it via team-viewer and learn from trail and error . I have so many things i wish to learn from the others to improve my knowledge and skills , this is a goal i plan 2 years ago and fail several projects and stop for exam and continue till this very year i believe nothing is impossible if you put in effort and have a not giving up mindset . Cheers ![/font] [/size] [center][size=12pt]Features:[/size] Combat system 80% Reputation system Correct combat styles fixed along with fighting unarmed is now handled Profile Viewing system Fading Hitmarks Lottery system Job system Prestige system Custom Vote interface
[img]http://i.imgur.com/PP0Jrcn.png[/img] [size=12pt]Minigames[/size] -Barrows -Duel arena [color=orange]-Barbarian Assault[/color] -Pest control -TzHarr Fight Cave -TzHarr Fight Pits -Castle war -Godwar -Fist of Guthix -Bounty Hunter
[size=12pt]Skills:[/size]
[img]http://imageshack.us/a/img248/428/woodcutting.png[/img] [size=12pt][color=blue]Woodcutting[/color][/size] ✓ Correct Hatchet Animations ✓ Correct Hatchet Requirements ✓ All Trees Can Be Cut ✓ Tree Stumps and Regrowth Timers
[img]http://imageshack.us/a/img585/8089/firemakingy.png[/img] [size=12pt]Firemaking[/size] ✓ All Logs Able To Be Burned ✓ Ashes After Log Burns Out X Correct Burning Timer (Doubt so) ✓ Clipping
[img]http://img809.imageshack.us/img809/8013/runecraftingn.png[/img] [size=12pt]Runecrafting[/size] ✓ Can Enter Altars With Talismans or Tiaras ✓ Can Craft All Runes ✓ Rune Multipliers ✓ Combination Runes ✓ Abyss X Pouches
[img]http://img194.imageshack.us/img194/6556/r8m2.png[/img] [size=12pt]Fishing[/size] ✓ All Fish Can Be Caught ✓ Correct Animations ✓ Correct Fish Requirements ✓ Fishing Trawler
[img]http://imageshack.us/a/img585/4393/thievingu.png[/img] [size=12pt]Thieving[/size]
Npc Pickpockect Stealing from Stall
[img]http://img853.imageshack.us/img853/6114/cookingni.png[/img] [size=12pt]Cooking[/size] ✓ All Fish Can Be Cooked ✓ Correct Timers ✓ Correct Burn Percentage ✓ Cooking Gauntlets ✓ Able To Cook On Ranges, Fires, Stoves, etc.
[img]http://i1251.photobucket.com/albums/hh541/SigmaTFR/Skills/Crafting-icon.png[/img] [size=12pt]Crafting[/size] ✓ Gem Cutting ✓ Jewelry Making ✓ Leather Making ✓ Leather Tanning
[img]http://img850.imageshack.us/img850/9995/3uo.png[/img] [size=12pt]Slayer[/size] All Slayer monster level requirements ✓All Slayer monster locations ✓Fremmennik Slayer Dungeon has 100% npcs ✓Slayer tower has 100% npcs + some other npcs for slayer ✓Tasks given are dependent on slayer level and combat level ✓Points given are dependent on task difficulty ✓Loading over 50 different individual slayer tasks ✓Ability to buy Slayer exp, Slayer's respite, Slayer darts and Broad arrows ✓Ability to use points to cancel tasks completely ✓Ability to remove tasks completely ✓Ability to delete removed tasks ✓Ability to find the location of slayer tasks
[img]http://i1251.photobucket.com/albums/hh541/SigmaTFR/Skills/Fletching-icon.png[/img] [size=12pt]Fletching[/size] ✓Bows and crossbows can be made ✓Handles 5, 10, X, All ✓Bolt Making includes onyx, dragonstone, etc ✓Bolt tip making ✓Shaft and stop making ✓limb creation support ✓string bow & crossbow support
[img]http://imageshack.us/a/img713/2460/tkw.png[/img] [size=12pt]Farming[/size] ✓All seed data from guam to torstol ✓Only one seed patch which is located at the skilling area ✓Includes raking and watering to complete the production process ✓Privately manipulates the farming patch into the herb patch object to pick from ✓seed patch updates from 60 squares away
Much more features will cut short there .
Images:
[img]http://puu.sh/274JJ/1e65e66a78.png[/img]
[img]http://puu.sh/1QHnT/722572b683.png[/img]
[img]http://puu.sh/1XIXz/2766428bf4.png[/img]
[img]http://puu.sh/1RGFN/4fac5f65bd.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/28tw3ex.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/351c0sw.png[/img]
[code]Applications: Skype: Proof of Work(links, projects, etc...): How many hours a day can you work?: Are you dedicated (Serious project): Why should I consider you: Anything else?:[/code]
[size=12pt][color=red]Main team selections: 1-2 Server sided programmers - Each doing different work but in the same project 1 Client sided programmer - Maybe be look for extra one more 1 Good graphic designer [color=red] Note:While working together its okay to make mistakes or asking questions , teamwork is what i want to see . I am not a expert programmer i am programmer who is willing to take the chance to learn from others[/size]
Thanks for your time Cheers ;)
Special Credits - Jason (His base)[/center]
